{
  "texts": [
    "We then ask the models to select the right definition.",
    "We derive a hallucinations index (HI), defined as the proportion of correctly generated definitions by each model (higher is better), based on the models' performance in this MCQ task.",
    "As seen in Table 8, the models' performances on the HI vary significantly.",
    "GPT-4 and ChatGPT lead the pack with exceptionally high scores of 98% and 95%, respectively.",
    "All three of our models perform better than the other open-source LLMs."
